00:23:34,010 --> 00:23:36,720
I'll defeat you for sure!

516
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:41,810
Before my eyes was just a tiny speck

517
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:41,810
jitsu wa chippoke datta to kizuita

518
00:23:36,720 --> 00:23:39,270
He seems to be in a strange mood.

519
00:23:39,270 --> 00:23:43,040
When he's shaking like that,
 you should just leave him alone.

520
00:23:41,810 --> 00:23:46,820
After all, meeting you so easily

521
00:23:41,810 --> 00:23:46,820
tatoeba kimi to deaeba kantan ni

522
00:23:43,040 --> 00:23:44,860
You're so cold to your own family!

523
00:23:44,860 --> 00:23:46,820
Wow, this is super high quality meat!

524
00:23:46,820 --> 00:23:48,320
Fumio-san went all out!

525
00:23:46,820 --> 00:23:51,400
Overturned my world

526
00:23:46,820 --> 00:23:51,400
sekai wa hikkurikaeru

527
00:23:48,320 --> 00:23:49,660
Thanks for the food!

528
00:23:49,660 --> 00:23:51,400
Hold up, you assholes!

529
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:56,520
Using sauce on that wagyu beef will destroy its delicate umami!

530
00:23:52,320 --> 00:23:58,460
There are so many things I don't know that I can't help but laugh

531
00:23:52,320 --> 00:23:58,460
shiranai koto darake de waraete kuruna

532
00:23:56,520 --> 00:23:58,060
Don't you have any respect for meat?!

533
00:23:58,060 --> 00:24:00,540
I-I'm so sorry, Nikumi-san!

534
00:23:58,460 --> 00:24:04,840
That means I can still grow much further

535
00:23:58,460 --> 00:24:04,840
madamada saki ni ikeru akashi da

536
00:24:00,540 --> 00:24:02,460
Don't call me Nikumi!

537
00:24:02,750 --> 00:24:06,420
The only one who can call me that is...

538
00:24:04,840 --> 00:24:10,170
I'm striding forward

539
00:24:04,840 --> 00:24:10,170
oikaketeta haruka tooku

540
00:24:06,420 --> 00:24:08,080
You bastard, look at what you're making me say!

541
00:24:08,080 --> 00:24:09,460
You asshole!

542
00:24:10,340 --> 00:24:15,680
Never surrendering my true feelings

543
00:24:10,340 --> 00:24:15,680
yuzurenai omoi mo tsurete

544
00:24:12,060 --> 00:24:15,470
All right, let me make a dish
 to cheer everyone up.

545
00:24:15,470 --> 00:24:17,430
I don't like the look in his eyes!

546
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:21,190
Toward a faraway peak

547
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:21,190
daremo shiranai itadaki wo

548
00:24:17,430 --> 00:24:19,080
Yukihira, stay put!

549
00:24:19,080 --> 00:24:21,600
You don't have to make anything, Souma-kun!

550
00:24:21,190 --> 00:24:23,810
That no one knows about

551
00:24:21,190 --> 00:24:23,810
mezashite iku

552
00:24:21,980 --> 00:24:24,440
But I've already made it, see?

553
00:24:23,810 --> 00:24:26,860
With everything on the line

554
00:24:23,810 --> 00:24:26,860
subete kakete

555
00:24:24,730 --> 00:24:26,400
Dig in!

556
00:24:27,270 --> 00:24:29,070
It's squid tentacles with yogurt.

557
00:24:29,360 --> 00:24:31,360
Oh, God!

558
00:24:31,360 --> 00:24:34,240
Not again!

559
00:24:37,740 --> 00:24:39,980
Thank you for the food!

